::Striker/Zenyak::

Striker ducks under a swing from Zenyak and punches him in the chest. Zenyak 
stumbles back.

Strker launches himself at Zenyak, grabbing him. The two bots fly into the 
covered entrance of the cave and the rocks fall outwards along with the two 
fighting bots, falling into the ocean.
